label: SENT
text:
I know I spoke to my mom's parents and her grandparents because they
   came to visit us, but it wasn't ... they would visit and stay for a week or
   two, but I really never felt anything because it'd be like, oh, they're
   your grandparents, but you never had much time to spend with them or have
   experiences with them, if it's such a limited time they're with you.
name: Melani
